select nspname from pg_namespace where nspname = 'agentz' limit 1;

create schema agentz;
set search_path to agentz;

create table agentz._models (
        id serial primary key,
        name text unique not null,
        table_name text unique not null,
        description text
    );

    create table agentz._columns (
        id serial primary key,
        name text  not null,
        type text not null,
        table_name text not null,
        "default" text,
        label text,
        unique(table_name, name)
    );

    create table agentz._roles (
        name text primary key,
        parentRole integer default 0, -- a column reference to agentz._roles itself. 0 means no parent
        password text,
        login text not null,
        description text not null
    );

    create table agentz._access_rules (
        id serial primary key,
        role text not null,
        method varchar(10) not null,
        url text not null
    );

    create table agentz._views (
        id serial primary key,
        name text unique not null,
        definition text unique not null,
        createdate timestamp with time zone default current_timestamp,
        updatedate timestamp with time zone default current_timestamp,
        description text
    );
